file.name: text2data.org-v3.1-swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  contact:
    x-twitter: Text2Data
  title: api.text2data.org
  version: v3.1
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - text
  x-logo:
    url: https://twitter.com/Text2Data/profile_image?size=original
  x-origin:
    - format: swagger
      url: http://api.text2data.org/swagger/docs/v3.1
      version: "2.0"
  x-providerName: text2data.org
paths:
  /api/Root:
    get:
      operationId: Root_Get
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/DocumentResult"
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/DocumentResult"
      tags:
        - Root
    post:
      operationId: Root_Post
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Document"
          text/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Document"
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Document"
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/DocumentResult"
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/DocumentResult"
      tags:
        - Root
servers:
  - url: http://api.text2data.org
components:
  schemas:
    Category:
      properties:
        CategoryName:
          type: string
        Score:
          format: double
          type: number
      type: object
    Document:
      properties:
        DocumentLanguage:
          type: string
        DocumentText:
          type: string
        IsTwitterContent:
          type: boolean
        PrivateKey:
          type: string
        Secret:
          type: string
        SerializeFormat:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        UserCategoryModelName:
          type: string
      type: object
    DocumentResult:
      properties:
        AutoCategories:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Category"
          type: array
        Citations:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/SentencePart"
          type: array
        CloudTagHTML:
          type: string
        CoreSentences:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Sentence"
          type: array
        DetectedLanguage:
          type: string
        DocSentimentPolarity:
          type: string
        DocSentimentResultString:
          type: string
        DocSentimentValue:
          format: double
          type: number
        Entities:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/SentencePart"
          type: array
        ErrorMessage:
          type: string
        Keywords:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/SentencePart"
          type: array
        NegativePhraseCount:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        NeutralPhraseCount:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        PartsOfSpeech:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/PartOfSpeech"
          type: array
        PositivePhraseCount:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        ResultTextHtml:
          type: string
        SlangWords:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/SlangWord"
          type: array
        Status:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        Subjectivity:
          type: string
        Summarization:
          type: string
        SwearWords:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/SlangWord"
          type: array
        Themes:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/SentencePart"
          type: array
        TransactionCurrentDay:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        TransactionDailyLimit:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        TransactionTotalCreditsLeft:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        TransactionUseByDate:
          format: date-time
          type: string
        UserCategories:
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Category"
          type: array
      type: object
    PartOfSpeech:
      properties:
        Action:
          type: string
        Object:
          type: string
        ObjectSentimentPolarity:
          type: string
        ObjectSentimentResultString:
          type: string
        ObjectSentimentValue:
          format: double
          type: number
        Subject:
          type: string
        Text:
          type: string
      type: object
    Sentence:
      properties:
        Relevance:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        SentenceNumber:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        SentimentPolarity:
          type: string
        SentimentResultString:
          type: string
        SentimentValue:
          format: double
          type: number
        Text:
          type: string
      type: object
    SentencePart:
      properties:
        KeywordType:
          type: string
        Mentions:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        SentencePartType:
          type: string
        SentenceText:
          type: string
        SentimentPolarity:
          type: string
        SentimentResult:
          type: string
        SentimentValue:
          format: double
          type: number
        Text:
          type: string
      type: object
    SlangWord:
      properties:
        SlangWordText:
          type: string
        SlangWordTranslation:
          type: string
      type: object
